  "prompt": "What is the first day at KMC, Manipal like?",
  "response": "The first day at Kasturba Medical College (KMC), Manipal, is an exciting and memorable experience for new students. It typically involves a mix of formalities, orientation, and getting to know the campus and your peers. Here\u2019s an overview of what you can expect:\n\n### 1. **Registration and Documentation**\n   - You\u2019ll start with registration, where you\u2019ll submit necessary documents (academic records, ID proofs, etc.).\n   - You\u2019ll receive your student ID card and other materials.\n\n### 2. **Welcome and Orientation**\n   - There\u2019s usually a formal welcome ceremony where the faculty and senior students introduce the college, its history, and its values.\n   - You\u2019ll be given an overview of the curriculum, rules, and expectations.\n\n### 3. **Campus Tour**\n   - Seniors or faculty members often guide newcomers around the campus, showing key locations like lecture halls, libraries, labs, the canteen, and other facilities.\n\n### 4. **Interaction with Seniors**\n   - Seniors may organize ice-breaking activities or informal sessions to help you get comfortable and build connections.\n\n### 5. **Introduction to Faculty**\n   - You\u2019ll meet your professors and department heads, who will explain the academic structure and support systems.\n\n### 6. **Batch Introductions**\n   - You\u2019ll get to know your batchmates, which is a great opportunity to make friends and start building your network.\n\n### 7. **Cultural and Extracurricular Introductions**\n   - KMC has a vibrant student community with numerous clubs and societies. You\u2019ll get an introduction to these and may even sign up for activities that interest you.\n\n### 8. **Practical Details**\n   - Information about the academic schedule, textbooks, and other logistics will be shared.\n\n### 9. **Hostel and Accommodation**\n   - If you\u2019re staying in a hostel, you\u2019ll settle into your room and get acquainted with the hostel rules and facilities.\n\n### 10. **First Day Traditions**\n   - Depending on the year, there may be some fun traditions or rituals organized by seniors to make the day memorable.\n\nThe first day at KMC, Manipal, is designed to help you transition smoothly into college life. It\u2019s a mix of formalities, excitement, and the beginning of a new chapter in your educational journey. Enjoy the experience and make the most of it!",
  "temperature": 1.0,
